{"tid":1089141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地方媽媽戀上常客　生了孩子夫才知戴綠帽","createTime":"2019-04-02T14:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T09:33:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70fdd4c266fc69fbc124260e809f491f2ea1deb3","tid":1089141,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"新北市已婚林姓女子和丈夫長期分居，卻愛上了一名常到她上班餐廳用餐的吳姓常客，更懷上了吳男的孩子，去年初生產後，丈夫才輾轉得知戴了綠帽，怒告2人涉犯通姦罪嫌。新北地檢署調查認為，吳男在林女刻意隱瞞下，一直都不知林女已婚，因此處分他不起訴，僅依通姦罪嫌起訴林女。<br />\n<br />\n起訴指出，林女（30多歲）和丈夫結婚10多年，也育有子女，但因為丈夫長期在外地工作的緣故，夫妻倆長期分居，平日在餐廳上班的林女，認識了常上門用餐的吳姓男子（約40歲），時日一久逐漸滋長愛苗，還懷上了吳男的孩子，前年底她向法院訴請與丈夫離婚獲判准後，隨即改嫁吳男，去年初便生下一名女嬰。<br />\n<br />\n她的前夫事後得知，才驚覺自己戴了綠帽卻被瞞在鼓裡，憤而控告2人涉犯通姦罪嫌。<br />\n<br />\n吳男出庭時喊冤，辯稱自己和林女交往、發生關係時，根本不知道對方早已是人妻，林女也不曾讓他到家裡，更不曾見過林女的身分證資料。林女也稱，自己隱瞞已婚、有小孩的事實和吳男交往，直到生產前吳男才得知。<br />\n<br />\n林女的前婆婆則證稱，她和林女先前都同住，只有曾在幾年前看過林女和一名男子，在住處外狀似親暱，但林女發現她之後，就趕快要那名男子離開，她不曾真正看過該名男子，孫子們也沒提過有陌生男人來找媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n檢方因此認為，林女在婚姻存續期間，刻意不讓婆婆、子女們知道她在外的交往情形，吳男辯稱不知道林女已婚應可採信，加上沒有證據可證明吳男在知道林女已婚後還嘿咻，因此處分吳男不起訴，僅依通姦罪嫌起訴林女。（游仁汶／新北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://usatthebiglead.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/kolo-toure-own-goal-against-fulham.gif?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fusatthebiglead.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F02%2Fkolo-toure-own-goal-against-fulham.gif%3Fw%3D1000&h=ce7114e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dfd9518a317dacca6f980af4fdd9a53f648a63c","tid":1089141,"uid":11067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"幅圖Owngoal<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe41ae5092220c53bdae546cee8e8b31ef32b89e","tid":1089141,"uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8dfd9518a317dacca6f980af4fdd9a53f648a63c","tid":1089141,"uid":11067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"幅圖Owngoal<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"因此處分吳男不起訴，僅依通姦罪嫌起訴林女。"},{"pid":"499b3f7a924eab5fd85467ebd640e15f95cebd87","tid":1089141,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T00:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada1faf207811bb0afd998a213905eab4abbcfaa","tid":1089141,"uid":74927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T01:16:31.000Z","msg":"台灣真係得風化案 會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef962acdd98cb5f5622acf50e53eae7cae39210","tid":1089141,"uid":182499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe41ae5092220c53bdae546cee8e8b31ef32b89e","tid":1089141,"uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8dfd9518a317dacca6f980af4fdd9a53f648a63c","tid":1089141,"uid":11067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"幅圖Owngoal<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"因此處分吳男不起訴，僅依通姦罪嫌起訴林女。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T01:28:49.000Z","msg":"台灣啲通姦罪有時都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0795ed717d0a9caf1857c3bc7ac9c5054825e0","tid":1089141,"uid":9887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ada1faf207811bb0afd998a213905eab4abbcfaa","tid":1089141,"uid":74927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T01:16:31.000Z","msg":"台灣真係得風化案 會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"依單係因為香港通姦唔係罪啫"},{"pid":"d38696d6a7df01ab303c01e99018df4aa67bfcfd","tid":1089141,"uid":117200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb0795ed717d0a9caf1857c3bc7ac9c5054825e0","tid":1089141,"uid":9887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ada1faf207811bb0afd99